data.description: Marvelous townhome with stylish amenities.  Two story, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home beautiful tile floors in living, kitchen and baths, carpet in all other areas.  Ceiling fans in every bedroom and living room.  Open living room & dining with wood burning fireplace and vaulted ceiling with wood beam accent.  Large yard with open patio and wood privacy fence.  Convenient location close to just about everything you would need.
